Installation instructions for openBibleViewer 0.5.4:
---------------------------


openBibleViewer requires:

- Qt-devel => 4.6
  or libqt-devel => 4.6
- cmake
- libz


Compile openBibleViewer:
---------------------------

tar -xjf openBibleViewer-0.5.4.tar.bz2
cd ~/openBibleViewer-0.5.4
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX='/usr' ..
make
sudo make install

